title: Wing is bringing drone delivery to 150 more Walmart stores
description:
Walmart and Wing plans to establish a network of over 270 drone delivery locations by 2027, stretching from Los Angeles to Miami.

The post Wing is bringing drone delivery to 150 more Walmart stores appeared first on The Robot Report.
